arStrings.szText: {c_important}Iron Maiden{/c} is now also a {c_important}Darkness{/c} Skill and deals Shadow damage. Enemies afflicted by your {c_important}Iron Maiden{/c} have a {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|%|]{/c} chance to be Stunned for {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} second when they deal direct damage.
